          <Heading><![CDATA[Security]]></Heading>
          <Description><![CDATA[<p> Villa San is kept safe and secure by two security staff working from 3pm to 7am. They will conduct regular patrols around the property, and also inside the grounds, unless otherwise requested by guests.</p>  ]]></Description>
